name: Silhoumesh YOU
description:
The Silhoumesh range  key chains features different silhouettes of characters inspired by people, animals and objects  which may remind you of those things in life which matters most. 

Silhoumesh YOU comes in He or She.  Ideal gift for yourself or for others as a little reminder of YOU. 

Take a look at the list below for different colours available to you. 

Want to make it extra special for that special someone?  We can personalise our silhoumesh by adding up to two letter initials to the design. 

Opening Promo!
"Like" us on Facebook with any purchases of our Silhoumesh characters and we will thank you with a free Griinprint clover key chain as a token of appreciation.
